    <h1>About Us</h1>

    <div class="article-body">
      <p>Florida Buzz is a digital publication owned and operated by Cartzilla LLC, providing Florida news, tourism updates, events, and lifestyle information.</p>

      <p>We cover the stories that matter to Florida residents and visitors alike — theme park updates, beach conditions, space launches, local events, and hidden gems around the state. Our goal is to keep readers informed with timely, accurate coverage sourced from official channels and summarized in our own words.</p>

      <h2>What we cover</h2>
      <p>Florida Buzz publishes daily articles across categories including theme parks, beaches, wildlife, local events, and general Florida news, along with in-depth evergreen guides designed to help residents and visitors get the most out of the Sunshine State.</p>

      <h2>Independent publication</h2>
      <p>Florida Buzz is an independently owned and operated travel and lifestyle publication. We are not affiliated with, endorsed by, sponsored by, or officially connected to The Walt Disney Company, Universal Destinations & Experiences, SeaWorld, LEGOLAND, or any other theme park, resort, or attraction we cover. All park, resort, and attraction names are the trademarks of their respective owners and are referenced here for informational and editorial purposes only.</p>

      <h2>Affiliate disclosure</h2>
      <p>Some of our articles and guides contain affiliate links, primarily through the Amazon Associates program. As an Amazon Associate, we earn from qualifying purchases made through these links, at no additional cost to you.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions or feedback can be sent to <a href="mailto:floridabuzzonline@gmail.com">floridabuzzonline@gmail.com</a>.</p>
